This project contains below mentioned features

Tech Stack : Spring Boot, JPA, Mockito, Junit5, Twilio, Javax Mail, Hibernate, MYSQL, Microservices, JWT, Spring Security, Spring Cloud Gateway, Kubernetes, Docker etc

1) User email verification system
2) Forgot password feature using twilio API
3) Microservices achitecture having API gateway level authentication and authorization using JWT Tokens (Auth0)
4) Eureka Discovery Server
5) RestTemplate for interservice communication
6) Mockito and JUNIT5 for testcases with code coverage above 90%
7) Spring Security.
